Package: reproj
Type: Package
Title: Coordinate System Transformations for Generic Map Data
Version: 0.4.2
Authors@R: person("Michael D.","Sumner", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
    "mdsumner@gmail.com", comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2471-7511"))
Description: Transform coordinates via from a specified source to a specified 
 target map projection. This uses the 'PROJ' library directly, by wrapping the 
 'PROJ' package (if functional), otherwise the'proj4' package. The 'reproj()' 
 function is generic, methods may be added to remove the need for an explicit 
 source definition. If 'proj4' is in use 'reproj()' handles the requirement for 
 conversion to and from radians where necessary. Used primarily for
 transformations with generic data formats and direct leverage of the underlying
 'PROJ' library. There are transformations that aren't possible with 'PROJ' that
 are provided for by using 'GDAL' library, so 'GDAL'-based software should be 
 used for thos. The 'PROJ' library is available at <https://proj.org/>.  
License: GPL-3
